two colleagues one of them wants to know
about where the other person is planning

00:06:49.919 --> 00:06:58.559
to rent an office so are you thinking of
renting a new office in London no I'd

00:06:58.559 --> 00:07:06.449
much rather be somewhere quieter oh yeah
any place in particular well I'm a huge

